item.title: Flax picker and banker bot!
item.dc:creator: @Cheesehunk Cheesehunk
item.description:
@Cheesehunk wrote:

No… just close all your SCAR’s. The plugins do not compile at runtime, they compile when you open SCAR. If you close all SCAR’s then re-open them the error should be fixed. If it isn’t re-download SRL, and make sure all SCAR’s are closed until the download is finished.

Read full topic
